{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"cad656dcea","title":"中国是否会出修正主义","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ec19c36cf2","index":0,"year":1966,"month":4,"day":null,"articleId":"cad656dcea"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji48","name":"毛泽东全集第48卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/48-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji48":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"dd571e5654","type":"title","text":"中国是杏会出修正主义","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"cad656dcea"},{"id":"32bfc37027","type":"paragraph","text":"中国会不会出修正主义当权派的问题，一是出，一是不出；一是早出，一是晚出。还是早出好，搞好了可能不出，在中国出修正主义是困难的。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"cad656dcea"},{"id":"e23449d5e0","type":"paragraph","text":"书记处也是分化的，彭、陆、杨、谭、罗等都当过书记处书记，是不断分化，合乎辩证法。有人怕得要死。不分化是主观愿望。中央有，各省也会有。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"cad656dcea"}],"page":{"id":"6f208269b9","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"cad656dcea","start":357,"end":357}}}},"__N_SSG":true}